Note: Runa AI Framework - Real-Time Strategy Execution Engine
Production-grade real-time strategy execution with live monitoring, adaptive control, and intelligent automation
Surpasses execution platforms, trading systems, and real-time decision engines :End Note

Note: Core execution types for comprehensive real-time strategy management
Type ExecutionType as Union containing:
    "real_time_execution",
    "batch_execution", 
    "event_driven_execution",
    "scheduled_execution",
    "adaptive_execution",
    "parallel_execution",
    "distributed_execution",
    "fault_tolerant_execution",
    "high_frequency_execution",
    "streaming_execution"

Note: Advanced execution engine with real-time capabilities
Type called "ExecutionEngine":
    "engine_id" as String,
    "engine_type" as ExecutionType,
    "execution_state" as String,
    "active_strategies" as Dictionary,
    "execution_queue" as List[Dictionary],
    "performance_monitors" as Dictionary,
    "risk_controls" as Dictionary,
    "circuit_breakers" as Dictionary,
    "execution_statistics" as Dictionary,
    "real_time_dashboard" as Dictionary,
    "engine_metadata" as Dictionary

